query:
SELECT p.id, p.status, g.id as gen_id, g.variation_group, g.front_view_url, g.left_view_url, g.back_view_url, g.right_view_url, g.created_at 
FROM projects p 
LEFT JOIN generations g ON p.id = g.project_id 
ORDER BY g.created_at DESC 
LIMIT 10;
